paṇidhīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:5.9":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.2:6.1":{"pli":"Sammāvācā maggo, sā ca anārammaṇā, natthi tāya āvaṭṭanā …pe… paṇidhīti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv10.2:6.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:6.3":{"pli":"Sammādiṭṭhi maggo, sā ca anārammaṇā, natthi tāya āvaṭṭanā …pe… paṇidhīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:6.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:6.5":{"pli":"sammāvācā maggo, sā ca anārammaṇā, natthi tāya āvaṭṭanā …pe… paṇidhīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:6.6":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:6.7":{"pli":"Sammāsaṅkappo …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:6.8":{"pli":"sammāvāyāmo … sammāsati … sammāsamādhi maggo, so ca anārammaṇo, natthi tassa āvaṭṭanā …pe… paṇidhīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:6.9":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.2:7.1":{"pli":"Sammākammanto …pe… ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv10.2:7.2":{"pli":"sammāājīvo maggo, so ca anārammaṇo, natthi tassa āvaṭṭanā …pe… paṇidhīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:7.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:7.4":{"pli":"Sammādiṭṭhi … sammāsaṅkappo … sammāvāyāmo … sammāsati …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:7.5":{"pli":"sammāsamādhi maggo, so ca anārammaṇo, natthi tassa āvaṭṭanā …pe… paṇidhīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:7.6":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.2:8.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv10.2:8.2":{"pli":"“maggasamaṅgissa rūpaṁ maggo”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:8.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:8.4":{"pli":"Nanu sammāvācā sammākammanto sammāājīvo maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:8.5":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:8.6":{"pli":"Hañci sammāvācā sammākammanto sammāājīvo maggo, tena vata re vattabbe—","html":"{}"},"kv10.2:8.7":{"pli":"“maggasamaṅgissa rūpaṁ maggo”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv10.2:8.8":{"pli":"Rūpaṁ maggotikathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"kv10.3":{"kv10.3:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<art